Company Summary
Aevi Genomic Medicine Inc. is focused on genomic medicine. The Company focuses on translating genetic discoveries into novel therapies. Its product candidates include AEVI-001 and AEVI-002 which are in clinical trial stage. Aevi Genomic Medicine Inc., formerly known as Medgenics Inc., is based in WAYNE, United States.   

















 


























